org.springframework.test.web.servlet.result

Class StatusResultMatchers

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.test.web.servlet.result.StatusResultMatchers

  • public class StatusResultMatchers
extends Object
    Factory for assertions on the response status. An instance of this class is typically accessed via MockMvcResultMatchers.status().
    Since:
    3.2
    Author:
    Keesun Baik, Rossen Stoyanchev
